<i>noun</i>: 충동 [충동], 조장 [조ː장], 선양 [서냥], 선동 [선동], 사주 [사ː주] <br>
<ul style="list-style-type:square">
<li><i>noun</i><br>
<dt>충동 [충동]</dt><br>
<dd>1. impulse; urge</dd><br>
<dd>순간적으로 어떤 행동을 하고 싶다고 느끼는 마음.</dd><br>
<dd>A feeling of wanting to do a certain thing suddenly.</dd><br>
<dd>2. instigation; abetment; incitement; stirring up</dd><br>
<dd>어떤 일을 하도록 남을 부추김.</dd><br>
<dd>An act of encouraging someone to do something.</dd><br>
<dt>조장 [조ː장]</dt><br>
<dd>incitement; instigation</dd><br>
<dd>좋지 않은 일을 더 심해지도록 부추김.</dd><br>
<dd>The act of exacerbating something bad in order to make it even worse.</dd><br>
<dt>선양 [서냥]</dt><br>
<dd>incitement; invigoration; stimulation</dd><br>
<dd>영향을 끼쳐 어떤 일을 일으킴.</dd><br>
<dd>The act of inciting, stimulating or provoking someone or something by one's influence.</dd><br>
<dt>선동 [선동]</dt><br>
<dd>instigation; incitement</dd><br>
<dd>다른 사람을 부추겨 어떤 일이나 행동을 하게 함.</dd><br>
<dd>The act of inciting a person to do something.</dd><br>
<dt>사주 [사ː주]</dt><br>
<dd>incitement; instigation; egging on</dd><br>
<dd>남을 부추겨 좋지 않은 일을 시킴.</dd><br>
<dd>An act of coaxing others to do wrongdoings.</dd><br>
</li>
</ul>